why_it_failed: All attempts fell short due to PostgreSQL's CTE optimization fence behavior. Workers 1-5 used non-materialized CTEs (default behavior in versions prior to 12), causing the planner to compute each CTE independently without cross-CTE join optimization or predicate pushdown. This prevented join order flexibility and forced nested-loop-like execution patterns.
